  18 Aug 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.6.ebuild,
  rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Stop using virtual/ruby-minitest, since it's now unbundled from 1.9 as
  well.

  08 Aug 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Use less existent nonexistent directory, fixing bug 321059.

*rdoc-2.5.9 (19 Jul 2010)

  19 Jul 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  22 May 2010; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.6.ebuild:
  Add REE18 support

  22 May 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -rdoc-2.4.3-r1.ebuild, rdoc-2.5.6.ebuild:
  Cleanup old versions, use new syntax.

*rdoc-2.5.6 (26 Apr 2010)

